    <title>Jupyter 添加 Python2 环境</title>
    <link href="/2022/12/22/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/Jupyter%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0Python2%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/"/>
    <url>/2022/12/22/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/Jupyter%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0Python2%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>基于Anaconda环境</p><p>安装 python2</p><p><code>conda create -n conda_python2.7 python=2.7</code></p><p>激活 python2</p><p><code>conda activate conda_python2.7</code></p><p>python2 安装 jupyter kernel</p><p><code>python -m pip install ipykernel</code><br> <code>python -m ipykernel install --user</code></p>]]></content>
    
    
